sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Arcade UI
    participant API as /query_memory
    participant MB as MemoryBundle
    participant L as Layers

    UI->>API: submit query
    API->>MB: query_memory
    MB->>L: fan out
    L-->>MB: results + status (ready/skipped/error)
    MB-->>API: aggregate + failed_layers
    API-->>UI: respond
